overview: "Macho Man" Randy Savage, Sting, and Lex Luger face The Outsiders and a mystery partner in the main event. Ric Flair battles Konnan for the WCW United States Championship. Rey Mysterio faces Psicosis. The Nasty Boys battle The Public Enemy. Plus, "Diamond" Dallas Page, The Giant and much more!
title: WCW Bash at the Beach 1996
